title: Gaia Series 104: Your Vote
summary: On Japan’s smallest village and in Tokyo’s suburbs, voters wrestle with loyalty, legacy and the fight to be heard in a crucial local election.

title: ByteDance says working to keep TikTok in US ‘under Chinese laws’ following Trump-Xi call
summary: China’s foreign ministry said in a statement late Friday night (Sep 19) that both presidents had a candid and in-depth exchange of views on the current state of China-US relations and other issues of mutual interest.

title: Public hospitals to streamline care teams, patients will see one 'principal doctor'
summary: Previously, patients with multiple conditions would have had to see multiple specialists, each with their own team.

title: Indonesia’s Lewotobi Laki-Laki volcano erupts as alert level raised
summary: The eruptions came after Indonesia's Geology Agency raised its alert level to the highest on Friday night (Sep 19).

title: Two bodies found in search for Freeport Indonesia workers trapped in mine, reports say
summary: Teams are still looking for other workers trapped underground in a copper mine for over 10 days, due to heavy mudflows.
